    "sn11.20:5.2": "kumbhi → kumbhe (bj); kumbhā (sya-all, km, pts1ed, mr); kumbhī (pts2ed) | kaḷopiyaṁ → khalopiyaṁ (bj) ",
    "sn11.20:5.3": "Paraniṭṭhitamesānā → paraniṭṭhitamesanā (sya-all, km, mr) ",
    "sn11.20:10.1": "pana → vatapadena (bj, sya-all, km, pts2ed) "
  },
